/tr></table><div class="funcprototype-spacer"> </div></div></div><div class="refsect1"><a id="parameters"></a><h2>Parameters</h2><div class="variablelist"><dl class="variablelist"><dt><span class="term"><em class="parameter"><code>coord</code></em></span></dt><dd><p>
                    Specifies a texture coordinate.
                    Must be one of <code class="constant">GL_S</code>, <code class="constant">GL_T</code>, <code class="constant">GL_R</code>, or <code class="constant">GL_Q</code>.
